title: Brett Soundtrack
description:
Brett Soundtrack

~*~	~*~	~*~	~*~	~*~
1: Poison - Alice Cooper. // I wanna love you but I better not touch.
2: Rocker - The 69 Eyes. // You&#039;ve got the blues but you can&#039;t have a romance.
3: The Checkered Demon - AFI. // I&#039;d like to bleed them all, when all is drained who shall hold? When mindless bodies screw tortured souls, will somebody be there to catch me when I fall?
4: Where No One Knows - Alexisonfire. // This is a love song, deal with it. I will beat my fist against my chest if only to prevent my heart from beating for you.
5: What If We Could - Blue October. // I&#039;m glad to say that we&#039;ve met, but I&#039;m sad to say that the circumstances weren&#039;t on our side.
6: Spit You Out - Bullet For My Valentine. // I am what I am! So I spit you out.
7: We&#039;re Equal - A. // You say it&#039;s not true, you finally want me, and this in&#039;t the first time, and this in&#039;t the last time.
8: All My Life - Foo Fighters. // Hey, don&#039;t let it go to waste,I love it but, I hate that taste.
9: Outsiders - Franz Ferdinand. // It&#039;s been some change but we&#039;re still outsiders, if everybody&#039;s here then hell knows we ride alone...
10: Razorblade Kiss - HIM. // The only way you can love me is to hurt me again. And again... and again... and again...
11: Perfect Skin - 69 Eyes. // You&#039;ve got a perfect skin. With a Devil&#039;s grin. Say hello to the pretty eyes. Say hello to the deadliest lies. You&#039;ve got the looks, baby, I could die.
12: Hateful - The Clash. // You see, I gotta go out again. Again? My friend, I gotta see that main man.
13: Dirty Life - Ima Robot. // I&#039;m comin&#039; for you, I want to shoot you up, I wanna do you, I wanna screw you up.
14: Wicked Game - HIM (Chris Isaak Cover). // What a wicked game you play, to make me feel this way, what a wicked thing to do, to let me dream of you.
15: Inside of You - Hoobastank. // It seems so obvious, there&#039;s something up with us, I smell the feeling from across the room.
16: Animals - Nickelback. // No, we&#039;re never gonna quit, ain&#039;t nothing wrong with it, just acting like we&#039;re animals.
17: I Love To Sin - Malice In Wonderland. // Helpless you can&#039;t change me. Will we always be apart?
18: Time Is Running Out - Muse. // You&#039;re something beautiful, a contradiction, I wanna play the game, I want the friction.
19: Frankenhooker - 69 Eyes. // I ain&#039;t looking for no head. From some fucking living dead. Dirty ass Frankenhooker. Got no class graveyard strutter. Dirty ass Frankenhooker. Down to kill tonight.
20: Demolition Lovers - My Chemical Romance. // I&#039;d end my days with you in a hail of bullets.
21: Domination - Pantera. // Domination consumes you then calls you a friend, it&#039;s a twisted fall, binds are like steel.
22: Blood Brothers - Papa Roach. // Survival of the fittest what it is, I got yo back, you got my back and that&#039;s the biz&#039;.
23: Taste In Men - Placebo. // Come back to me a while, change your style again.
24: Your Kind of Lover - Queen. // We gotta talk it out man to man, make each other nderstand, right now a little happiness would be fine.
25: To Be Loved - Papa Roach. // I want domination, I want your submission. I see you&#039;re not resisting to this temptation.
26: Tainted Love - Marilyn Manson. // Don&#039;t touch me, please, I cannot stand the way you tease.
27: Beautiful - HIM. // Just one look into your eyes, one look and I&#039;m crying. Cos you&#039;re so beautiful.
28: Remedy - Seether. // You&#039;ll be the death of me.
29: Soil - Hear me. // Please hear me,the pain that I feel happiness was nowhere to be found. Please hear me I scream out for help, have you even heard a word of mine.
30: LL Cool J - Hey Lover. // Hey lover, this is more than a crush.
31: A Goodnight&#039;s Sleep - The Starting Line. // A better slumber, was in your arms, spent tangled up in you.
32: Alive With the Glory of Love - Say Anything. // When I watch you, wanna do you, right where you&#039;re standing, right on the foyer, on this dark day, right in plain view.
33: Baby, It&#039;s Fact - Hellogoodbye. // Baby, it&#039;s fact, that our love is true the way black is black, and blue is just blue, my love is true, It&#039;s a matter of fact.
34: The Bad Touch - Bloodhound Gang. // You and me baby ain&#039;t nothin&#039; but mammals, so lets do it like they do on the discovery channel.
35: Never Say Die - 69 Eyes. // The darkest days are through. Once you taste my love you&#039;ll make it. Though I&#039;m standing by your side. I feel so lonely I could ry.
36: Sharpest Lives - My Chemical Romance. // Your kiss and I will surrender, the sharpest lives are deadliest to lead.

~*~	~*~	~*~	~*~	~*~
OBS! Track #7 is not included, since I could never find the god damned song!
